2 bananas
2 Oreo packs
5 gels
6 müsli bars
5 peanut butter, jam, banana, syrup, double sandwiches
200g nuts
4 caffeine pills
4 water stops —> ~18 bottles of water. 
9 electrolyte tablets
2 carbohydrate tablets
1 monster white</div>

